I21Pub. L. 111ÿ09358, title II, ÿ1A202, Jan. 4, 2011, 124 Stat. 3993, provided that:

I21``(a) T4Sense of CongressK._It is the sense of Congress that NASA [National Aeronautics and Space Administration] is uniquely positioned to interest students in science, technology, engineering, and mathematics, not only by the example it sets, but through its education programs.

