I89. Acquiring United States Government property and services

I11(a) T4General Requirements and ConsiderationsK._(1) The Secretary of Transportation shall facilitate and encourage the acquisition by the private sector and State governments of_

I12(A) launch or reentry property of the United States Government that is excess or otherwise is not needed for public use; and

