Q04

I11(2) In acting under paragraph (1) of this subsection, the Secretary shall consider the commercial availability on reasonable terms of substantially equivalent launch property or launch services or reentry services from a domestic source, whether such source is located on or off a Federal range.

I11(b) T4PriceK._(1) In this subsection, ``direct costs'' means the actual costs that_

I12(A) can be associated unambiguously with a commercial launch or reentry effort; and

I12(B) the Government would not incur if there were no commercial launch or reentry effort.

