I89. Enforcement and penalty

I11(a) T4ProhibitionsK._A person may not violate this chapter, a regulation prescribed under this chapter, or any term of a license issued or transferred under this chapter.

I11(b) T4General AuthorityK._(1) In carrying out this chapter, the Secretary of Transportation may_

I12(A) conduct investigations and inquiries;

I12(B) administer oaths;

I12(C) take affidavits; and

I12(D) under lawful process_

I13(i) enter at a reasonable time a launch site, reentry site, production facility, assembly site of a launch vehicle or reentry vehicle, crew or space flight participant training site, or site at which a payload is integrated with a launch vehicle or reentry vehicle to inspect an object to which this chapter applies or a record or report the Secretary requires be made or kept under this chapter; and

