I12(1) may not adopt or have in effect a law, regulation, standard, or order inconsistent with this chapter; but

I12(2) may adopt or have in effect a law, regulation, standard, or order consistent with this chapter that is in addition to or more stringent than a requirement of, or regulation prescribed under, this chapter.

