I89. Data policy for Landsat 7

I11(a) T4LandsatK 7 T4Data PolicyK._The Landsat Program Management, in consultation with other appropriate United States Government agencies, shall develop a data policy for Landsat 7 which should_

I12(1) ensure that unenhanced data are available to all users at the cost of fulfilling user requests;

I12(2) ensure timely and dependable delivery of unenhanced data to the full spectrum of civilian, national security, commercial, and foreign users and the National Satellite Land Remote Sensing Data Archive;

