I89. Tasks of Commission

I11A Commission established pursuant to this chapter shall, to the extent possible, undertake the following tasks:

I12(1) T4InvestigationK._Investigate the incident.

I12(2) T4CauseK._Determine the cause of the incident.

I12(3) T4Contributing factorsK._Identify all contributing factors to the cause of the incident.

I12(4) T4RecommendationsK._Make recommendations for corrective actions.

I12(5) T4Additional findings or recommendationsK._Provide any additional findings or recommendations deemed by the Commission to be important, whether or not they are related to the specific incident under investigation.

I12(6) T4ReportK._Prepare a report to Congress, the President, and the public.

