I89. Powers of Commission

I11(a) T4Hearings and EvidenceK._A Commission or, on the authority of the Commission, any subcommittee or member thereof, may, for the purpose of carrying out this chapter_

I12(1) hold such hearings and sit and act at such times and places, take such testimony, receive such evidence, administer such oaths; and

